profile: Bronson Johnson Seamless Eavestroughs has quickly become one of Ottawa's top choices for your water evacuation requirements!  We specialize in Eavestrough (Gutter) installation.  BJSE also provides Leaf Screen (Leaf Guard) protection.  We have exclusive rights to GT Premium Micro Leaf Screen which is ideal for metal roofing systems.   Our mission is to be Referred by our Customers, Revered by our Competitors and Respected by our Community.
products: We only use 0.032" thick 5 inch Seamless Eavestrough; Exclusive rights to the Hidden Hanger used in our installations; Leaf Guard, Leaf Screen; Environmentally friendly Rain Barrel installation.  Also, ask about our product that eliminates  "Tiger Stripes" which occur on white and light coloured eaves.

specialities: B.J.S.E is the only company in Ottawa to specialize in the installation of.032" thick Aluminum Eavestroughs which is significantly stronger than standard .023", .024" and .027" material used by our competitors. profile:
At Excel Building & Roofing we are "On top of what matters most" with specialties in residential and commercial roofing and renovations in the Ottawa and surrounding area. As an Ottawa contractor we deliver the best in quality, workmanship and insist the job is done right the first time. 

With all the chaos that comes with our day to day lives we know that any home project, needed or wanted, can seem both overwhelming and out of reach. At Excel Building & Roofing we are with you every step of the way.

Our team has over 25 years combined experience in the field and we are extremely motivated to make a change in the way this city views the construction industry. "A lot of companies are faceless and in it for a quick buck. This isn't just a "job" for us and our clients are not just "another project", this is how we make our living and support our family." 

Call us picky, but quality is a prerequisite and a bad job is simply unacceptable. We do not rush jobs and choose our materials and team very carefully to ensure it is done right the first time.

When you choose Excel you receive:
- A Green Company, we recycle 100% of materials removed from your home.
- Superior quality and workmanship   
- Always above standard materials and installation
- Constant management - during and after installation inspections 
- No hidden fees or extras, what we quote you is what you pay.

*** Ottawa Roofing experts***

profile:
MARKELANGELO'S ROOFING serves the greater Ottawa area.  We are a professional and trustworthy company with a proven track record. We have fully trained, certified employees who specialize in specific installation procedures and focus 100% on quality control to ensure your satisfaction with the final product. 
 
As a testament to our exceptional level of service, our clients eagerly recommend us to friends and family. In fact, we built Markelangelo’s solely through word of mouth.

We are very aware of how our business impacts the environment. We contribute by participating in recycling programs available at local landfills. All garbage, shingles, metal and wood are separated before we take our dump trailers to these landfills. Each waste product is then put into its appropriate area of the landfill and processed. We save approximately a thousand tonnes of material being buried in landfills every year.

profile:
Rest Assured Roofing specializes in asphalt shingled roof removals and new roof installations. Our goal is to provide homeowners with an incredible experience from the moment they get in touch with us, to the final clean-up.

We offer an industry-leading, 10-year workmanship warranty that has helped us provide properties with an extensive range of roofing services such as residential roofing Ottawa, Emergency roof repair, guaranteeing excellent customer satisfaction. To extend the longevity of your roof, we utilize the highest quality material to ensure that you receive an incredible, and efficient roofing experience.

Fully Insured
Qualified in Certainteed installations as well as products
48-Hour Estimate Guarantee
24/7 Emergency Service

WARRANTY INFORMATION: 
We have passed both written testing and quality inspections to become certified with Certainteed. This allows us to provide our customers with an extended 50 year Surestart warrantee. What does that mean?
Well, SureStart offers the best coverage you can get on your  new roof and here is what it provides:

- 100% of materials:
All shingles required to repair or replace the defective product will be provided free. No exceptions.

- 100% of labor:
All labor required to repair defective shingles or apply new shingles to replace the defective shingles will be paid by CertainTeed, based on local fair market value for labor.

- Additional costs:
The cost of flashing, metal work, tear-off and disposal are included.

- Without prorating the costs: 
The cost of materials and labor are not prorated or otherwise reduced.

profile:
A1 Professional Roofing provides professional roofing services in Ottawa and surrounding area. 
We service the greater Ottawa area as well as west to Stittsville/Kanata and as far east as Rockland.

As a premiere roofing company in the Ottawa area we invite you to explore our site to learn more about our free estimates and full re-roofing replacement services.

Our best selling products are the long lasting and architecturally laminated Cambridge lifetime fiberglass shingles by IKO. We also install the GAF – Timberline products.

Please contact us today to discuss your best shingle option. 
An A1 Professional Roofing expert will be pleased to discuss your needs and recommend the best products for your re-roofing job.

613-731-0849
products:
Our laminated fibreglass shingles add architectural interest that boosts your curb appeal.  Choose from a huge array of colours which coordinate perfectly with your home’s style.
Our feature products are the IKO Cambridge and Dynasty Lifetime Architectual shingle. These shingles are constructed with some of the heaviest fibreglass mats in the industry for their class, engineered to withstand the elements for years making them among the most durable shingles you can buy.
services:
RESIDENTIAL AND COMMERCIAL ROOFING
We specialize in residential re-roofing and have been servicing the Ottawa region for over 18 years.

A1 Pro Roofing guarantees an expert installation. Our team of experienced staff and skilled tradesmen deliver a stunning result every time.

We specialize in servicing single-family homes as well as semi-detached and townhouses.

Leaving you with peace of mind for you and your family.

 Specializing in metal and asphalt roofs means we can give you exactly what you are looking for. Guaranteed.

profile:
Joseph Niles started his roofing career in August 2012. He worked for a variety of different companies in Ottawa, some large and some small.
Over the years he gained experience from several veterans of the trade, working all seasons installing asphalt shingles.

 However, no matter where he was working he always felt like he was worth more and wanted to provide better service than the companies today.
With a great knowledge and love for asphalt shingle roofing and its products, he was able to open a family business founded on trust, reliability and honesty in June of 2018 with his wife Rachelle.

His dream is to train as many people as he can and re populate the community of roofers in this city and hopefully one day grow enough to franchise and continue his work elsewhere.


  

We offer a warranty unlike any other
5 and 10-year warranty available
5- year complimentary snow maintenance 
Complimentary  5-year spring inspections
Blow off damage for 105/kmhr winds
Repairs at a 30% discounted price after warranty expires (only applicable to 10 year warranty)
When we do your roof you become part of our family ,and we treat our family well.


  

Why Choose Us?
We take photos ,before ,during and after all jobs and provide them to the customer at no cost
Your new flawess roof is featured on our Facebook page and website gallery for the world to see
Offer a variety of Packages to meet your budget and needs !
Integrity, honesty , trust and amazing workmanship
We take our time to make sure the job is done right and no harm come to your roof or property, we respect your investment !
Knowing that our team will be there to take care of your roof for years to come  !
Lets be frank,

 in Ottawa you have A LOT of options for roofing services.
However , with Niles Roofing you get treated like family , we believe that honesty goes along way. As a roofing business it is our mission to  to be a reliable source of information and trusted quality work. 

Remember ,

THERE IS NO SUBSTITUTE FOR QUALITY

profile:
Roofing Now is a smaller, local Ottawa roofing company with over 1000 happy customers and steadily growing. We are eager to please and provide top-notch customer service; this personalized attention paired with our competitive pricing is what sets us apart from the larger roofing contractors in Ottawa.

Roofing Now is proud to service the Ottawa area. Our repairs have outlived many warranties by at least two times.We provide professionally trained roofing installers to view, assess and quote on roofing repairs and roof replacements. Our certified installers are employees of Roofing Now, many of whom have been working a long time with the company. Roofing Now carries full insurance coverage including WSIB, working at heights and HST registration.

For reviews and testimonials from homeowners in the Ottawa area, please check out our reviews page. To schedule a free no obligation inspection, please contact us or call 613-265-8881 or click here to request a free quote.
services:
Roofing Now offers  24 Hour Emergency Roof Repair.
Ottawa Area Emergency Roofing Services
We know that when you have a roofing emergency most times you don’t have time to wait. Call us right away and we’ll help diagnose the problem while we prepare an immediate plan of action for repairing your Roof.
Roofing Now provides rapid roofing repairs & roofing installations, for shingled and steel roofs in Ottawa Valley area.
specialities: We will perform all work in an effective,professional and in a friendly manner. We always comply with local and provincial roofing code and regulations.

profile:
CLS Roofing Company is your flat roofing specialist for residential, commercial and industrial buildings. With 27 years of experience, the management at CLS roofing has been focusing on the flat roof industry while still offering other contracting services.
 
Our trained and skilled roofing contractors specialize in handling all of your roofing needs: we offer emergency roofing service, disaster clean up service, roofing ventilation upgrades, asphalt shingles, metal shingles and panels, cedar shingles, and other roofing services to commercial, residential and industrial clients all throughout the Ottawa area.
